statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets;
SELECT property_name, property_type, location FROM real_estate_assets WHERE total_units > 10;
SELECT property_name, total_units, fraction_unit_price FROM real_estate_assets WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' ORDER BY total_units DESC;
SELECT id, property_name, location, fraction_unit_price FROM real_estate_assets WHERE location LIKE '%City%' ORDER BY fraction_unit_price ASC;
SELECT property_name, property_type, total_units FROM real_estate_assets WHERE fraction_unit_price > 500000 ORDER BY property_name ASC, total_units DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' ORDER BY fraction_unit_price DESC, total_units ASC
SELECT property_name, location FROM real_estate_assets WHERE location LIKE '%City%' AND total_units >= 50
SELECT MAX(total_units) AS max_units, MIN(fraction_unit_price) AS min_price FROM real_estate_assets
SELECT property_name, location, total_units * fraction_unit_price AS total_value FROM real_estate_assets WHERE total_units * fraction_unit_price > 500000 ORDER BY total_value DESC
SELECT DISTINCT property_type FROM real_estate_assets ORDER BY property_type

SELECT owner_id, asset_id, percentage_owned FROM FractionalOwnership WHERE percentage_owned >= 50 ORDER BY percentage_owned ASC;

SELECT RealEstateAssets.address, FractionalOwnership.percentage_owned, TokenTransactions.tokens_transferred FROM RealEstateAssets JOIN FractionalOwnership ON RealEstateAssets.asset_id = FractionalOwnership.asset_id JOIN TokenTransactions ON RealEstateAssets.asset_id = TokenTransactions.asset_id WHERE TokenTransactions.transaction_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY TokenTransactions.tokens_transferred DESC;

SELECT owners.owner_name, owners.email, real_estate_assets.asset_name FROM owners JOIN ownership ON owners.owner_id = ownership.owner_id JOIN real_estate_assets ON ownership.asset_id = real_estate_assets.id;

SELECT transactions.transaction_id, transactions.transaction_type, ownership.shares_owned FROM transactions JOIN ownership ON transactions.ownership_id = ownership.ownership_id WHERE transaction_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT location, SUM(total_shares) AS total_shares FROM real_estate_assets GROUP BY location;

SELECT t.token_name, o.owner_name FROM Tokens t JOIN Owners o ON t.owner_id = o.owner_id WHERE t.token_value > 1000 ORDER BY t.token_name ASC;
SELECT p.property_name, COUNT(f.fractional_id) AS num_fractions FROM Properties p LEFT JOIN FractionalOwnership f ON p.property_id = f.property_id GROUP BY p.property_name HAVING num_fractions > 5;
